            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a new energy hydrogen production dynamic green ammonia synthesis system and an operation method thereof. The system comprises a renewable energy hydrogen production device, an air separation nitrogen production device, an ammonia synthesis compressor, a start-up heating furnace, an ammonia synthesis tower, a plurality of ammonia synthesis adjusting towers, a plurality of heat exchangers and a plurality of adjusting valves, and all the devices are communicated according to a system operation process. When the system is started, nitrogen is firstly introduced to preheat the system, and the load of the ammonia synthesis tower is gt; when 30%-50%, the system operates normally; when the new energy fluctuates, the output is reduced, and the load of the ammonia synthesis tower is reduced to 10-50%, ammonia gas is synthesized through the first ammonia synthesis adjusting tower and returns to the ammonia synthesis tower so as to maintain the normal operation of the tower; when the load of the first ammonia synthesis adjusting tower is reduced to 10-50%, the ammonia synthesis tower stops running, ammonia gas is synthesized through the second ammonia synthesis adjusting tower and returns to the first ammonia synthesis adjusting tower to maintain normal running of the first ammonia synthesis adjusting tower, and so on. According to the invention, continuous and controllable operation of the ammonia synthesis process can be maintained, and finally off-grid new energy hydrogen production dynamic synthesis of green ammonia is realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种新能源制氢动态合成绿氨系统及其运行方法。该系统包括可再生能源制氢装置、空分制氮装置、氨合成压缩机、开工加热炉、氨合成塔、多个氨合成调节塔、多个热交换器和多个调节阀；各设备间按照系统运行过程相连通。系统启动时，首先通入氮气对系统预热，氨合成塔负荷>30～50%，系统正常运行；当新能源发生波动出力下降，导致氨合成塔负荷下降至10～50%时，通过第一氨合成调节塔合成氨气返回氨合成塔以维持该塔正常运行；当第一氨合成调节塔负荷下降至10～50%时，氨合成塔停止运行，通过第二氨合成调节塔合成氨气返回第一氨合成调节塔以维持该塔正常运行，依次类推。本发明能够保持氨合成过程的连续可控运行，最终实现离网型新能源制氢动态合成绿氨。"
                }
            ]
